							<div class="richtext"><p>We allow our customers to review our products and post these reviews on our website. These reviews provide valuable feedback and help other customers make purchasing decisions. We designed our review system to be as transparent and helpful as possible.</p><h1>How Reviews are Collected</h1><p>We send a request for a review 21 days after the purchase date. Customers can review any of the products they purchased.</p><p>We post all reviews immediately on our website unless an automated system flags for inappropriate language. We manually review any flagged reviews and post them if appropriate.</p><h1>Changing Reviews</h1><p>We allow reviewers to change their reviews upon request. If you want to change a review, please contact our customer service team to edit your review.</p><h1>Compensation Policy</h1><p>We do not compensate reviewers for their reviews.</p><h1>Review Removal</h1><p>We reserve the right to remove:</p><ul><li><p>Reviews that contain inappropriate language or content</p></li><li><p>Reviews posted by or advertising competitors</p></li><li><p>Reviews that contain links to other websites</p></li><li><p>Reviews with personally identifiable information</p></li></ul><p></p><p>We reserve the right to adjust our review policies as needed.</p></div>
